    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Managun Wizard</strong>, you play as a mage armed with a powerful magic shotgun. Face waves of unique enemies, using quick thinking and smart tactics to survive. Battle through fast-paced rounds in a cursed dungeon where each victory brings you closer to breaking the endless cycle of rebirth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283300/extras/8871d92cd66c3f8d38ccff3baef43b62.poster.avif?t=1748927213\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283300/extras/8871d92cd66c3f8d38ccff3baef43b62.webm?t=1748927213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283300/extras/8871d92cd66c3f8d38ccff3baef43b62.mp4?t=1748927213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Combat</strong>: Fight intense battles with magic and gunplay, combining spells and shotgun blasts to defeat a wide range of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enemy Variety</strong>: Each enemy type has distinct behaviors, forcing you to adapt your strategy with every wave.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283300/extras/0c380eca0ba44a4b6fe3dad3b530f4cf.poster.avif?t=1748927213\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283300/extras/0c380eca0ba44a4b6fe3dad3b530f4cf.webm?t=1748927213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283300/extras/0c380eca0ba44a4b6fe3dad3b530f4cf.mp4?t=1748927213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrades</strong>: Unlock and upgrade abilities and weapons at the end of each round to make your wizard stronger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Progression</strong>: Advance through increasingly difficult rounds in your quest to escape the cursed dungeon.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Challenge</strong>: Each defeat sends you back to the start, but with new tactics and upgrades, you can push further next time.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283300/extras/37fb7d175847f144807aaa74aa4af2a1.poster.avif?t=1748927213\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283300/extras/37fb7d175847f144807aaa74aa4af2a1.webm?t=1748927213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283300/extras/37fb7d175847f144807aaa74aa4af2a1.mp4?t=1748927213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mutations</strong>: Stack different upgrades to cause your character to mutate, gaining unique bonuses and boosters.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Word to Player</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Managun Wizard</strong></i><strong> is in active development, with new features and improvements planned. The description will be updated as the game evolves to reflect new content and gameplay changes.</strong></p>",
